text: Gujarat Titans is a cricket franchise based in Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India. The Titans compete in the Indian Premier League (IPL). Founded in 2021, Gujarat Titans' home ground is Narendra Modi Stadium in Ahmedabad. The franchise is owned by CVC Capital Partners. The team is captained by Shubman Gill and coached by Ashish Nehra. ==References== Category:2021 establishments in India Category:Indian Premier League teams
